# DUAL LICENSE NOTICE

This repository contains two types of content, each governed by different licenses:

## 1. CODE LICENSE: Apache License 2.0

All code, scripts, implementations, and technical artifacts in this repository are licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

### Apache License 2.0 (Summary)

- You may use, copy, modify, and distribute the code
- You may use the code for commercial purposes
- You must include the original copyright and license notice
- You must state significant changes made to the code
- The software is provided "as is" without warranty

Full Apache 2.0 license text: https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

---

## 2. RESEARCH ORE LICENSE: CC BY-NC-ND 4.0

All research content, specifications, protocols, academic papers, and creative artifacts (collectively "Research Ore") are licensed under Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International.

### CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 (Summary)

- **Attribution (BY)**: You must give appropriate credit
- **NonCommercial (NC)**: You may not use for commercial purposes
- **NoDerivatives (ND)**: You may not distribute modified material

Full CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/

