## 4. CONTENT CLASSIFICATION

### Code (Apache 2.0)
- `*.py`, `*.js`, `*.ts`, `*.sh`, `*.yml`, `*.yaml` files
- `/irp_swarm_console/` directory
- `/irp-accesspanel/js/` directory
- `/.github/workflows/` directory
- Implementation scaffolding in `/protocols/*/implementation/`

### Research Ore (CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 + Spirit Clause)
- `*.md` files (except README files explaining code)
- `*.xml` files (protocol packets, schemas)
- `*.json` files (specifications, configurations)
- `/protocols/` directory (specifications)
- `/kernel/` directory (governance documents)
- `/archive/` directory (chronicles, handoff packets)
- `/docs/` directory (documentation, papers)
- `/skills/` directory (skill specifications)
- `GOVERNANCE_CODEX_LAW.md`

